videos.description: Billy Bahl connects with Sam Martin for a 28-yard strike to set up the Redhawks first and goal.
videos.headline: Bahl hits Martin inside the red zone

videos.description: Kenny Young scores the game's first touchdown on a 7-yard run to extend the lead for Miami, Ohio.
videos.headline: Young gallops for a Redhawks TD

videos.description: Kyle Vantrease hits Kamathi Holsey on a 37-yard deep ball for Buffalo.
videos.headline: Holsey leaping catch puts the Buffalo in the red zone

videos.description: Kyle Vantrease to Anthony Johnson for a 8-yard touchdown to put Buffalo on the scoreboard.
videos.headline: Vantrease connects with Johnson for TD

videos.description: Ikeem Allen forces  Bufflao's Kyle Vantrease to fumble and Joshua Allen recovers to set up Miami (Ohio).
videos.headline: Allen and Allen combine for the takeaway for Miami (Ohio)
